## <a id="2-1-6"></a> v2.1.6

**Release Date: November 7, 2019**

### Features

New features and changes in this release:

* The minimum RAM for the Pivotal Anti-Virus Mirror VM is set to 1.5&nbsp;GB instead of 1&nbsp;GB.
* Adds TLS support for custom mirrors.
For more information, see [Configure Anti-Virus](./install.html#configure).

### Resolved Issues

This release fixes the following issues:

* Anti-Virus Mirror deployments no longer fail in air-gapped environments.
* The clamd app no longer forwards duplicate logs.

