## <a id="2-1-3"></a> v2.1.3

**Release Date: October 23, 2019**

### Features

New features and changes in this release:

* Adds mutual TLS from Anti-Virus Mirror to the <%= vars.product_short %> hosts.
<br>For more information, see [Changing the Port Used by <%= vars.product_short %> and Anti-Virus Mirror](./changing-ports.html).
* Adds support for excluding instance groups.
<br>For more information,
    see the [List of instance group names that will be excluded from deployment](./install.html#configure) field.
* Updates golang dependency to v1.13.1 for both Linux and Windows

